    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nutricibus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Cassius <lb n="2"/>Verinus <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Poet</abbr><ex>ovionensium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fabr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>pro <expan><abbr>IIvir</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> et Donnia Maximilla <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iux</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>pro salute <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> Cassi Severi fili
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Im erhaltenen Teil des Bildfeldes eine Frau, die ein kleines Kind nach rechts hin zu einer sitzenden Nutrix reicht; links eine Dienerin(?). Die Inschrift befindet sich unterhalb des Reliefs.</p>
            </div>
